=== Implementation Notes ===

- Added finalizedBars map (key: broker+canonical+period) to BarAggregator.
- LoadFinalizedBars accepts pre-queried map from CH (SELECT MAX close_ts per key).
- IngestExternalBar method: checks bar.CloseTsUnixMs <= finalizedBars[key],
  skips with metric increment if so; otherwise updates finalized ceiling.
- AddTick (real-time path): updates finalizedBars on each emitted bar,
  ensuring live bars always raise the ceiling (never blocked by finality).
- spill_replay bar path: documented that ReplacingMergeTree ORDER BY provides
  sufficient dedup; full IngestExternalBar check exercised via backfiller path.
- Created metrics.go with barSkippedFinalized atomic counter.

Files changed:
- backend/internal/mdgateway/bar_aggregator.go (finalizedBars + IngestExternalBar + AddTick update)
- backend/internal/mdgateway/spill_replay.go (finality comment)
- backend/internal/mdgateway/metrics.go (new, barSkippedFinalized counter)
